@startuml
title EduMind（智教）系统整体架构图（C4 分层简版）

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #34495E
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #5B6B7A
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #F8FBFF
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #5B6B7A

actor "教师 / 学生 / 管理员" as User

rectangle "前端访问层\nReact Web 前端\n教师端 / 学生端 / 文件库 / 历史记录" as Frontend
rectangle "网关接入层\nNginx / API Gateway\nHTTPS / WebSocket / 负载均衡" as Gateway
rectangle "后端业务层\nFastAPI 服务集群\n认证、教学、学习、文件、异步任务" as Backend
rectangle "RAG 与 AI 能力层\n资料解析、向量检索、Agent 编排、模型网关" as AI
database "数据存储层\n关系数据库 / 向量数据库 / Redis / 对象存储" as Storage
rectangle "部署运维层\nDocker / Kubernetes / 监控日志" as Deploy

User --> Frontend : 使用系统
Frontend --> Gateway : HTTPS / WebSocket
Gateway --> Backend : API 调用
Backend --> AI : 生成任务 / RAG 查询
Backend --> Storage : 业务数据读写
AI --> Storage : 资料切片 / 向量检索 / 生成成果
Deploy ..> Gateway
Deploy ..> Backend
Deploy ..> AI
Deploy ..> Storage

note right of AI
RAG 主流程：
资料上传 -> 解析切分 -> 向量入库
-> 权限过滤检索 -> 构造 Prompt
-> 模型生成
end note

note bottom of Backend
普通文本任务可同步返回；
播客、视频、幻灯片等长任务
通过队列和 WebSocket 返回进度。
end note

@enduml

/'
以下为旧版详细组件图，已注释停用。
保留仅用于后续需要恢复细节时参考。
title EduMind（智教）分布式 RAG 系统整体架构图

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #34495E
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #5B6B7A
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #F8FBFF
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #5B6B7A
skinparam QueueBorderColor #5B6B7A

actor "教师" as Teacher
actor "学生" as Student
actor "教研/管理员" as Admin

cloud "公网 / 校园网" as Net

node "客户端层" {
  component "Web 浏览器\nReact 19 + Vite + TypeScript" as Browser
  component "教师端工作台\nLessonPlan / Quiz / Paper / Slides / TeachingVideo" as TeacherUI
  component "学生端工作台\nSmartNotes / FlashCards / WrongBook / Podcast / Speaking" as StudentUI
  component "文件库与历史记录\nFileLibrary / TeachingRecords / LearningRecords" as CommonUI
}

node "接入层 / 边缘层" {
  component "CDN / 静态资源服务" as CDN
  component "Nginx / Ingress\nHTTPS / 反向代理 / 负载均衡" as Nginx
  component "API Gateway\n路由聚合 / 限流 / CORS / WebSocket 转发" as Gateway
}

node "分布式业务服务层\nFastAPI 微服务集群" {
  component "Auth Service\n注册登录 / Token / RBAC / 双角色隔离" as AuthSvc
  component "User & Session Service\n用户资料 / 会话 / scope 管理" as UserSvc
  component "File Service\n上传 / 下载 / 文件元数据 / 权限校验" as FileSvc
  component "Chat & RAG API\n资料增强问答 / Prompt 组装 / 流式回答" as RagApi
  component "Teacher Service\n教案 / 测验 / 试卷 / 教学记录" as TeacherSvc
  component "Student Service\n笔记 / 卡片 / 错题本 / 学习记录" as StudentSvc
  component "Multimodal Service\n幻灯片 / 播客 / 口语 / 教学视频" as MultiSvc
  component "Bilibili Service\nB 站视频学习与备课" as BiliSvc
  component "WebSocket Service\n任务进度 / 流式输出 / 状态通知" as WsSvc
}

queue "消息队列\nRedis / Celery broker" as MQ
queue "任务调度器\nCelery / Redis / generation-worker" as Scheduler

node "Agent 与异步 Worker 集群" {
  component "BaseAgent\n统一模型调用与工具封装" as BaseAgent
  component "LessonPlanAgent" as LessonAgent
  component "NoteAgent" as NoteAgent
  component "QuizAgent / PaperAgent" as QuizAgent
  component "FlashcardsAgent" as FlashAgent
  component "KnowledgePointAgent\n薄弱知识点识别" as KnowledgeAgent
  component "SlidesAgent" as SlidesAgent
  component "PodcastAgent\nTTS + ffmpeg" as PodcastAgent
  component "SpeakingAgent\nASR / 口语评价" as SpeakingAgent
  component "TeachingVideoAgent\n脚本 / 配音 / 视频合成" as VideoAgent
}

node "RAG 知识处理链路" {
  component "文档解析器\nPDF / DOCX / Markdown / TXT" as Parser
  component "清洗与切分\n去噪 / Chunk / 元数据标注" as Chunker
  component "Embedding Service\n向量化 / 批处理 / 缓存" as EmbedSvc
  database "Vector DB\npgvector\nchunk_id / embedding / metadata" as VectorDB
  component "Retriever\nTopK 检索 / 权限过滤 / 多路召回" as Retriever
  component "Reranker\n重排 / 去重 / 引用片段选择" as Reranker
  component "Prompt Builder\n角色自适应 / 资料引用 / 输出约束" as PromptBuilder
}

node "模型与外部 AI 能力层" {
  component "LLM Gateway\n模型路由 / Key 管理 / 熔断降级" as LLMGateway
  component "通用大模型 API\nOpenAI / DeepSeek / 通义 / 智谱等" as CloudLLM
  component "本地教育模型\nLoRA Adapter / 轻量问答" as LocalLLM
  component "TTS / ASR 服务" as SpeechAI
  component "图像/视频生成服务" as MediaAI
  component "Bilibili MCP Bridge" as BiliBridge
}

node "数据与存储层" {
  database "关系数据库\nPostgreSQL / pgvector\nusers / sessions / chats / permissions" as RDB
  database "Redis\nSession 缓存 / 限流 / 任务状态" as Redis
  database "对象存储\nMinIO / OSS / 本地 storage\nPDF / 图片 / 音频 / 视频" as ObjectStore
  database "JSON 结果库\n教案 / 笔记 / 测验 / 播客 / 视频任务结果" as JsonStore
  database "日志与审计库\n访问日志 / 模型调用 / 内容审核记录" as AuditDB
}

node "运维与安全层" {
  component "Docker / Kubernetes\n服务编排 / 横向扩展 / 滚动发布" as K8s
  component "Prometheus + Grafana\n指标监控 / 告警" as Monitor
  component "ELK / Loki\n日志检索 / 链路排错" as Logs
  component "内容安全与合规\n敏感词 / 未成年人保护 / 人工审核" as Safety
}

Teacher --> Browser
Student --> Browser
Admin --> Browser
Browser --> TeacherUI
Browser --> StudentUI
Browser --> CommonUI
Browser --> Net
Net --> CDN
Net --> Nginx
CDN --> Browser : 静态资源
Nginx --> Gateway : HTTPS API / WebSocket

Gateway --> AuthSvc
Gateway --> UserSvc
Gateway --> FileSvc
Gateway --> RagApi
Gateway --> TeacherSvc
Gateway --> StudentSvc
Gateway --> MultiSvc
Gateway --> BiliSvc
Gateway --> WsSvc

AuthSvc --> RDB
AuthSvc --> Redis
UserSvc --> RDB
FileSvc --> ObjectStore
FileSvc --> RDB
TeacherSvc --> JsonStore
StudentSvc --> JsonStore
TeacherSvc --> MQ : 生成任务
StudentSvc --> MQ : 生成任务
MultiSvc --> MQ : 多模态任务
WsSvc --> Redis : 读取任务状态
WsSvc --> Browser : 进度推送 / 流式输出

MQ --> Scheduler
Scheduler --> LessonAgent
Scheduler --> NoteAgent
Scheduler --> QuizAgent
Scheduler --> FlashAgent
Scheduler --> KnowledgeAgent
Scheduler --> SlidesAgent
Scheduler --> PodcastAgent
Scheduler --> SpeakingAgent
Scheduler --> VideoAgent

LessonAgent -up-|> BaseAgent
NoteAgent -up-|> BaseAgent
QuizAgent -up-|> BaseAgent
FlashAgent -up-|> BaseAgent
KnowledgeAgent -up-|> BaseAgent
SlidesAgent -up-|> BaseAgent
PodcastAgent -up-|> BaseAgent
SpeakingAgent -up-|> BaseAgent
VideoAgent -up-|> BaseAgent

FileSvc --> Parser : 文件入库后触发解析
Parser --> Chunker
Chunker --> EmbedSvc
EmbedSvc --> VectorDB
Chunker --> ObjectStore : 原文 / sidecar text / 切片缓存
Chunker --> RDB : 文档元数据 / 权限元数据

RagApi --> Retriever
Retriever --> VectorDB
Retriever --> RDB : user_id / scope / role 权限过滤
Retriever --> Reranker
Reranker --> PromptBuilder
PromptBuilder --> LLMGateway
BaseAgent --> PromptBuilder : 资料增强上下文
BaseAgent --> LLMGateway : 模型调用
LLMGateway --> CloudLLM
LLMGateway --> LocalLLM

SlidesAgent --> MediaAI
PodcastAgent --> SpeechAI
PodcastAgent --> ObjectStore
SpeakingAgent --> SpeechAI
VideoAgent --> MediaAI
VideoAgent --> SpeechAI
VideoAgent --> ObjectStore
BiliSvc --> BiliBridge

TeacherSvc --> AuditDB
StudentSvc --> AuditDB
RagApi --> AuditDB
LLMGateway --> AuditDB : 调用日志 / 成本 / 错误
Safety --> Gateway : 请求侧内容检查
Safety --> LLMGateway : 生成侧安全策略
Monitor --> Gateway
Monitor --> MQ
Monitor --> Redis
Logs --> AuditDB
K8s --> Gateway
K8s --> AuthSvc
K8s --> RagApi
K8s --> Scheduler

note right of Retriever
RAG 查询流程：
1. 用户选择资料或输入问题
2. 按 user_id / scope / role 过滤资料
3. TopK 检索 + Rerank
4. 构造带引用片段的 Prompt
5. LLM 生成并通过 WebSocket 返回
end note

note bottom of RDB
现有 PostgreSQL/pgvector 可作为单机原型。
分布式部署建议迁移为 PostgreSQL / pgvector，
并保留 Redis、对象存储和向量库作为独立服务。
end note

@enduml
